"allure: command not found": You need to install the Allure command-line tool.
Mac (Homebrew): brew install allureWindows (Scoop): scoop install allure
Manual: Download the binaries from Maven Central, unzip them, and add the bin folder to your system PATH.
Blank Report / Loading Issues: Do not try to open the index.html file directly from your file explorer (e.g., double-clicking it).
Browsers block the necessary AJAX calls for security reasons. You must use allure open or allure serve to view it correctly.

